## Evaluation: t7-9-b-prep-restore-visual-harness

### Execution Results (Codex-verified)
- cargo test --workspace: PASS (277 passed, 0 failed)
- cargo test -p sim-test harness_: PASS (87 passed, 0 failed)
- Anti-circular check: CIRCULAR — screenshot assertions pass even when screenshot files are not written
