### Threshold Review
- Assertion 1 (gdscript_file_parses_without_errors): OK
- Assertion 2 (evidence_directory_produces_exactly_seven_artefacts): ISSUE: fresh headless run produced 5 files, not 7
- Assertion 3 (pipeline_bypass_line_present_and_terminal_token_valid): OK
- Assertion 4 (all_four_self_verifying_assertions_resolve_to_visual_ok): ISSUE: checklist reported `VISUAL_OK` while screenshots were missing
